:wall_base_cavity_insul: %= codes.lookup("Opaque Envelope Requirements | Climate Zone #{climate_zone}", "Walls Above Grade | Mass Heavy", "Cavity R-Value")['R-IP']
:wall_base_cont_insul: %= (1/codes.lookup("Opaque Envelope Requirements | Climate Zone #{climate_zone}", "Walls Above Grade | Metal Framed", "Maximum U-Factor")-1.49)['R-IP']
:roof_base_cont_insul: %= (1/codes.lookup("Opaque Envelope Requirements | Climate Zone #{climate_zone}", "Roofs | Metal Buildings", "Maximum U-Factor")-0.78)['R-IP']
:floor_base_cont_insul: %= ((1/codes.lookup("Opaque Envelope Requirements | Climate Zone #{climate_zone}", "Floors | Other", "Maximum U-Factor"))-4.261)['R-IP']
